<HI>Grelot</HI> my approbation of those excellent Delineations
which he is now making publick to the world. He has so
well represented to the life those places which I have
seen in <HI>Constantinople,</HI> in the <HI>Archipelago,</HI> in <HI>Cyprus,</HI>
and in <HI>Syria,</HI> that casting my eyes upon his delineations of
some other places where I have not been, I am apt to
believe that I see the Originals themselves.</P>
