to turn them toward <HI>Kobl&egrave;,</HI> where the <HI>Mirabe</HI>
or <HI>Mahumetan</HI> Altar stands.</P>
<P><HI>B.</HI> The <HI>Mirabe</HI> or <HI>Maharah,</HI> like a Nich in the Wall,
where the Alcoran is kept. On the right and left hand
stand two large Candlesticks, and in each a Taper of
