his Devotions.</P>
<P><HI><GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">.</HI> The Gallery leading to the Closet.</P>
<P><HI>D.</HI> Two low Terraces or Balcones for the Singers and
Moderators of the peoples Voices, which they call
