</FIGURE></P>
<P><HI>E.</HI> The Preachers Pulpit, wherein there is a Sermon
<HI>A-la-turquesca</HI> Wednesdays and Fridays.</P>
<P><HI>F.</HI> The Windows of the Church.</P>
<P><PB N="122" REF="80">
f. The Windows of the <HI>Domo's,</HI> low, and giving
little light.</P>
