<P><HI>O.</HI> The three large Windows of the Quire, and <HI>San|ctum
Sanctorum.</HI> In the Rounds between the Win|dows
are the names of eight great Prophets of the
<HI>Turkish</HI> Law.</P>
<P><HI>P.</HI> The mouth of the great Cistern under the Church,
whence they fetch Water to cool the Musselmen, when
